#

Spinach Salad with Strawberries and Almonds

10 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Tree NutsDairy (if feta is used)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickFresh

Description

A refreshing spinach salad with sweet strawberries and crunchy almonds, perfect for a light meal.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach leaves: 4 cups
  • strawberries, sliced: 1 cup
  • sliced almonds: 1/2 cup
  • feta cheese, crumbled (optional): 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
